<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 22:08:05 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>10 月 7 日效应：以色列人离开以色列，散居海外的犹太人取代了他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-october-7-effect-the-israelis-leaving-israel-and-the-diaspora-jews-replacing-them/00000191-b6b7-d13c-a39b-bebff9830000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日以来，由于反犹太主义、反犹太复国主义、与以色列的团结、对战争和民主崩溃的恐惧，或者仅仅是高昂的生活成本，数以万计的犹太人离开家园，往返于以色列。 21世纪第三个十年又回到漂泊的生活？</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 21:20:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-october-7-effect-the-israelis-leaving-israel-and-the-diaspora-jews-replacing-them/00000191-b6b7-d13c-a39b-bebff9830000</guid></item><item><title>“剩下的就是费城”：以色列各地数千人抗议加沙人质释放协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/thousands-protest-across-israel-for-gaza-hostage-release-deal/00000191-c36c-de0a-afd5-db6c4e3d0000</link><description>数以千计的以色列人在特拉维夫、耶路撒冷、海法和其他城市举行示威，要求达成释放人质协议，内塔尼亚胡批评内塔尼亚胡数天内第二次混淆了 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击的日期</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 20:34:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/thousands-protest-across-israel-for-gaza-hostage-release-deal/00000191-c36c-de0a-afd5-db6c4e3d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方调查西岸巴勒斯坦被拘留者在监狱中遭受性虐待的指控</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-investigates-palestinian-detainees-allegation-of-sexual-abuse-in-prison/00000191-c27e-d870-a59d-e67fb2200000</link><description>西岸的一名巴勒斯坦居民声称，自加沙战争开始以来，以色列监狱工作人员多次对他进行性虐待和身体虐待，并且无视他的医疗请求</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 19:53:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-investigates-palestinian-detainees-allegation-of-sexual-abuse-in-prison/00000191-c27e-d870-a59d-e67fb2200000</guid></item><item><title>拜登，如果你真的想了解内塔尼亚胡，听听他用希伯来语说的话</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/biden-if-you-really-want-to-understand-netanyahu-listen-to-what-he-says-in-hebrew/00000191-c1f2-db84-a3bd-ebfee9380000</link><description>对于总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡来说，加沙的费城路线现在是摆脱任何可能的停火和人质协议的最快途径。美国政府会知道，如果它在过去几个月里更加关注他的希伯来语演讲</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 19:11:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/biden-if-you-really-want-to-understand-netanyahu-listen-to-what-he-says-in-hebrew/00000191-c1f2-db84-a3bd-ebfee9380000</guid></item><item><title>像乌克兰一样：真主党开始用 FPV 赛车无人机攻击以色列军队</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/like-ukraine-hezbollah-begins-attacking-israeli-forces-with-fpv-racing-drones/00000191-c338-d870-a59d-e77bec490000</link><description>乌克兰战场上最致命的武器之一最近出现在真主党与以色列的冲突中，而且极其难以拦截：第一人称视角无人机，可以让飞行员从飞机的角度观察</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 18:41:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/like-ukraine-hezbollah-begins-attacking-israeli-forces-with-fpv-racing-drones/00000191-c338-d870-a59d-e77bec490000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的地图显示了以色列“从河流到海洋”。这绝非偶然</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-05/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-map-shows-israel-from-the-river-to-the-sea-its-no-accident/00000191-c2a8-d09f-ab91-debc90e60000</link><description>在总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的“费城”演讲中，还有一个很少有人注意到的信息，尽管它根本没有隐藏</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 18:13:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-05/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-map-shows-israel-from-the-river-to-the-sea-its-no-accident/00000191-c2a8-d09f-ab91-debc90e60000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯以色列记者因悲痛的被杀人质遭受种族主义袭击而向警方投诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/arab-israeli-journalist-files-police-complaint-following-torrent-of-racist-attacks/00000191-c2a1-d09f-ab91-debd319f0000</link><description>以色列阿拉伯电视主持人露西·阿哈里什（Lucy Aharish）充满激情的独白哀悼在加沙被谋杀的六名人质在网上被分享后，这位记者在社交媒体和她的个人手机上收到了大量种族主义攻击</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 17:57:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/arab-israeli-journalist-files-police-complaint-following-torrent-of-racist-attacks/00000191-c2a1-d09f-ab91-debd319f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列、美国、英国和欧洲国家签署具有里程碑意义的国际人工智能条约</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-u-s-britain-and-european-countries-sign-landmark-international-ai-treaty/00000191-c2cd-d3f8-adf5-deefe7660000</link><description>《人工智能公约》要求公司保护人权和民主制度，同时保持透明度、隐私和平等，并将主要适用于公共部门</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 17:45:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-u-s-britain-and-european-countries-sign-landmark-international-ai-treaty/00000191-c2cd-d3f8-adf5-deefe7660000</guid></item><item><title>“我不敢告诉我的大屠杀幸存者朋友我要去德国，但她完全同意”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/i-was-afraid-to-tell-my-holocaust-survivor-friend-i-was-going-to-germany/00000191-c251-d549-a9ff-e371c8bf0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一名年轻的以色列妇女持有前往柏林进行学位后旅行的单程机票，以及不顾一切仍计划在以色列抚养孩子的年轻父母</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 17:06:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/i-was-afraid-to-tell-my-holocaust-survivor-friend-i-was-going-to-germany/00000191-c251-d549-a9ff-e371c8bf0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第335天：埃及军事首长对加沙边境进行突击检查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-335-egypts-military-chief-holds-surprise-inspection-of-gaza-border/00000191-c31b-df27-a9b9-fb9bd3560000</link><description>美国官员告诉记者，以色列和哈马斯同意 90% 的停火条款 ■ 美国驻以色列特使卢驳斥了内塔尼亚胡关于拟议停战协议第一阶段要求以色列从费城走廊撤军的说法 ■ 国际刑事法院首席检察官卡里姆·汗国防部长加兰特表示，对内塔尼亚胡发出搜查令的请求是基于他亲自审查的证据 ■ 这是战争开始 335 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 17:00:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-335-egypts-military-chief-holds-surprise-inspection-of-gaza-border/00000191-c31b-df27-a9b9-fb9bd3560000</guid></item><item><title>对以色列占领加沙的恐惧促使埃及与土耳其走得更近</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/fear-of-potential-occupation-of-gaza-pushes-egypt-closer-to-turkey/00000191-c28e-d09f-ab91-de9ef0280000</link><description>开罗仍然被认为是美国推动的反伊朗联盟的重要组成部分，但随着对以色列的批评不断增加，这一防御屏障正在崩溃</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 16:11:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/fear-of-potential-occupation-of-gaza-pushes-egypt-closer-to-turkey/00000191-c28e-d09f-ab91-de9ef0280000</guid></item><item><title>解释：为什么以色列没有起诉哈马斯 10 月 7 日暴行的嫌疑人？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-delaying-indictments-of-oct-7-suspects-over-open-legal-questions/00000191-c2a2-d2ba-adb1-e6ab30800000</link><description>美国联邦当局已对哈马斯高级官员提出指控，但在以色列，对数千名巴勒斯坦嫌疑人的起诉却被推迟。从国际法考虑到以色列人质的命运，以下是尚未提出指控的原因</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 15:49:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-delaying-indictments-of-oct-7-suspects-over-open-legal-questions/00000191-c2a2-d2ba-adb1-e6ab30800000</guid></item><item><title>在内塔尼亚胡失态后，以色列重申摩洛哥对西撒哈拉的主权</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-reaffirms-moroccan-sovereignty-of-western-sahara-after-netanyahu-gaffe/00000191-c25b-d870-a59d-e67b87690000</link><description>在新闻发布会上，内塔尼亚胡展示了一张大型中东和北非数字地图，其中摩洛哥南部被标记为西撒哈拉。以色列于 2023 年承认摩洛哥对争议领土的主权，以换取恢复外交关系</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 15:01:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-reaffirms-moroccan-sovereignty-of-western-sahara-after-netanyahu-gaffe/00000191-c25b-d870-a59d-e67b87690000</guid></item><item><title>瑞安航空暂停以色列航班至 10 月 26 日，跳过高需求假期季节</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/ryanair-halts-israel-flights-until-october-26-skipping-high-demand-holiday-season/00000191-c230-d2ba-adb1-e6b98bdc0000</link><description>德国汉莎航空将于周四恢复飞往特拉维夫的航班；对于消费者来说，瑞安航空的决定将减少假期期间的航班供应，可能会推高机票价格</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 14:26:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/ryanair-halts-israel-flights-until-october-26-skipping-high-demand-holiday-season/00000191-c230-d2ba-adb1-e6b98bdc0000</guid></item><item><title>“时间不多了；美国驻以色列特使在人质协议推动中警告称，将没有生命可救</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/there-wont-be-lives-left-to-save-u-s-envoy-to-israel-warns-in-hostage-deal-push/00000191-c1e4-dd1b-a7db-f7fef14f0000</link><description>卢大使反驳了内塔尼亚胡关于以色列国防军从加沙和费城走廊全面撤军是协议初始阶段的一部分的说法：“协议中没有提到费城走廊；起草框架时甚至没有考虑到这一点”</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 11:35:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/there-wont-be-lives-left-to-save-u-s-envoy-to-israel-warns-in-hostage-deal-push/00000191-c1e4-dd1b-a7db-f7fef14f0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡受到全球谴责，忙于躲避破坏人质交易的指控</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/rattled-by-global-rebuke-netanyahu-scrambles-to-fend-off-charges-of-sabotaging-gaza-deal/00000191-c140-d2e0-a7d5-ddd270f10000</link><description>除了与外媒举行新闻发布会外，内塔尼亚胡还派了自己的心腹罗恩·德尔默前往美国媒体讨论人质谈判，因为总理担心美国媒体会更多地关注人质家属对他的批评</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 10:34:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/rattled-by-global-rebuke-netanyahu-scrambles-to-fend-off-charges-of-sabotaging-gaza-deal/00000191-c140-d2e0-a7d5-ddd270f10000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查显示，大多数以色列人支持审查加沙战争社交媒体帖子，揭露犹太与阿拉伯之间的分歧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/poll-majority-of-israelis-back-censoring-gaza-war-posts-exposing-jewish-arab-divide/00000191-c119-de0a-afd5-d959c4d20000</link><description>民意调查发现，政治分歧进一步影响了对审查制度的看法。在以色列右翼人士中，76% 的人希望封锁支持加沙平民的帖子，而左翼人士中只有 25% 的人愿意</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 09:27:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/poll-majority-of-israelis-back-censoring-gaza-war-posts-exposing-jewish-arab-divide/00000191-c119-de0a-afd5-d959c4d20000</guid></item><item><title>卡梅尔·盖特的家人授权播放哈马斯被囚禁的视频：“内塔尼亚胡判处她死刑”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/carmel-gats-family-authorizes-airing-captivity-video-netanyahu-sentenced-her-to-death/00000191-c0a9-dffe-abf9-fdff26310000</link><description>39 岁的盖特 (Gat) 来自贝埃里基布兹 (Kibbutz Be&amp;#39;eri)，于 10 月 7 日被绑架。获释的人质称，她主持瑜伽和冥想课程，以帮助他们保持理智。她计划在人质协议的初始阶段被释放</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 06:04:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/carmel-gats-family-authorizes-airing-captivity-video-netanyahu-sentenced-her-to-death/00000191-c0a9-dffe-abf9-fdff26310000</guid></item><item><title>“哈里斯同情亲哈马斯的民主党人”：副总统拜登在共和党犹太会议上抨击以色列政策</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/on-first-night-of-gop-jewish-confab-speakers-assail-biden-and-harris-over-israel-policies/00000191-c02b-d2e0-a7d5-ddfb24a30000</link><description>拉斯维加斯共和党犹太大会的代表们指责现任政府为哈马斯 10 月 7 日的袭击提供了便利，让反犹太主义在国内愈演愈烈，并且未能勇敢地面对伊朗</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 03:38:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/on-first-night-of-gop-jewish-confab-speakers-assail-biden-and-harris-over-israel-policies/00000191-c02b-d2e0-a7d5-ddfb24a30000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯发布被谋杀的以色列裔美国人质赫什·戈德堡-波林的囚禁视频</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article-live/u-s-can-ensure-israeli-security-if-idf-withdraws-from-philadelphi-route-official-says/00000191-bffd-d26b-abfd-bfff57690000</link><description>数千人在特拉维夫集会争取人质交易 ■ 白宫：哈马斯是最大障碍 ■ 国际刑事法院首席检察官为内塔尼亚胡辩护，勇敢的逮捕令：“我已经看到证据” ■ 慕尼黑袭击以色列领事馆：枪手是当局已知的伊斯兰分子 ■ 以色列国防军：火箭弹、八架无人机发射到以色列北部；无人员伤亡 ■ 加沙卫生部：以色列拒绝协调医疗队入境进行脊髓灰质炎疫苗接种 ■ 美国高级官员：如果以色列国防军从费城撤军，我们可以确保以色列的安全</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 02:31:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article-live/u-s-can-ensure-israeli-security-if-idf-withdraws-from-philadelphi-route-official-says/00000191-bffd-d26b-abfd-bfff57690000</guid></item></channel></rss>